currrentProductList.imageAlt: Birch Moisturizing Sunscreen UVLock SPF 45+ Broad Spectrum
currrentProductList.productName: Birch Moisturizing Sunscreen UVLock SPF 45+ Broad Spectrum
currrentProductList.description: This sunscreen doubles as a moisturizer, which is perfect for those who want to keep their skin hydrated while avoiding the damaging effects of the sun! The product highlights that it is made with birch sap, which is supposed to keep your skin hydrated all day. It also doesn't leave a whitecast on me, nor leave my skin feeling greasy. It also is unscented, which is perfect for those of us who are sentitive to fragrances.

currrentProductList.imageAlt: Dr. G pH Cleansing Red Blemish Clear Soothing Foam
currrentProductList.productName: pH Cleansing Red Blemish Clear Soothing Foam
currrentProductList.description: A low pH cleanser that's perfect to use in the mornings. It gently cleanses your skin, leaving your skin feeling taut and smooth. This product is great for those with acne-prone and sensitive skin, as its unique 10-cica complex formula immediately soothes the skin and leaves it feeling fresh!

currrentProductList.imageAlt: Round Lab 1025 Dokdo Toner Jumbo Size 500ml
currrentProductList.description: A great basic hydrating toner that immediately sinks into your skin, leaving it feeling plump and fresh! It contains ingredients to not only maintain your skin's moisture balance, but also helps to reducde the amount of sebum and gently exfolates any remaining dead skin cells from cleansing.

A great basic oil cleanser that removes all makeup, sunscreen, and impurities from your skin without stripping it. This has always been a staple in my routine, and I find myself going back to this product time and time again.

currrentProductList.imageAlt: Heartleaf Quercetinol Pore Deep Cleansing Foam 150ml
currrentProductList.productName: Heartleaf Quercetinol Pore Deep Cleansing Foam
currrentProductList.description: I use this as my second cleanser. It deeply cleanes your pores and leaves your skin feeling refreshed!

currrentProductList.imageAlt: SKIN1004 Madagascar Centella Poremizing Clear Toner
currrentProductList.description: I use this as my evening toner! It not only wipes away any remaining residue and dead skin cells on your face after cleansing, but also minimizes your pores while doing so.

This essence/serum is watery, so it sinks into your skin immediately. I originally got this because I thought the bear on the bottle was cute, but I can see that it's reducing the amount of redness I have on my skin.

I got this along with the Murad Rapid Relief Acne Spot Treatment one day when I was breaking out badly, and I didn't want to order products from overseas. Whenever I breakout, I apply this 2-3 times a day with the spot treatement, and slap a pimple patch on my blemishes. After a few days, they're completely gone! A little bit goes a long way, so this will last you a good while.

currrentProductList.imageAlt: Beauty of Joseon Calming Serum Green Tea + Panthenol 30mL
currrentProductList.description: This soothing serum works to reduce redness and calm down irritated skin. My skin feels less oily and looks brighter the next day after using this product!

I just got this product, so not much to say about this yet. I enjoyed the other Murad products I've used in the past, so I have high hopes for this one! It contains retinol, which is supposed to help with fine lines and wrinkles, reducing the signs of aging.

currrentProductList.imageAlt: SKIN1004 Madagascar Centella Probio-Cica Bakuchiol Eye Cream 20ml
currrentProductList.productName: Madagascar Centella Probio-Cica Bakuchiol Eye Cream
currrentProductList.description: This eye cream contains an ingredient called bakuchiol, which is a supposed vegan alternative to retinol. It helps to reduce the appearance of fine lines, wrinkles, and dark cirles. I enjoy the applicator shape, which is shaped to really spread the product evenly under your eyes.

currrentProductList.imageAlt: SOME BY MI AHA BHA PHA 30 Days Miracle Cream 60g
currrentProductList.productName: AHA BHA PHA 30 Days Miracle Cream
currrentProductList.description: One of my holy grails of all time! This soothes my skin and helps to clear up any breakouts I have. It contains AHA, BHA, and PHA, which are all chemical exfoliants that help to remove dead skin cells and unclog pores. I use this as my evening moisturizer, and it leaves my skin feeling soft and smooth by the next morning. It also helps to repair your skin barrier, leaving it looking fresh and healthy!

I have tried multiple more expensive lip exfoliators, and this works just as well. I have the orange creamsicle flavor, which smells amazing and tastes even sweeter! I love how it's in a stick form, so I don't risk contaminating the product with my fingers.

currrentProductList.imageAlt: Dr. Jart+ Jelly Bear Lip Mask
currrentProductList.description: A good basic lip mask. I originally got it because I thought the packaging was cute. There is no scent, so if you're looking for that, this lip mask is the one for you.

This is advertised as a "conditioning milk", but honestly it's just a very light moisturizer. I use this after my morning toner. It's formulated with 7% peach fruit extract, ceramide, hyaluronic acid, vitamin B12, and niacinamide to moisturize and brighten the skin.

currrentProductList.imageAlt: L'Occitane en Provence Scalp Night Serum
currrentProductList.description: I use this whenever I shampoo. It's supposed to nourish your scalp, promoting healthy hair growth.

I use this whenever I shampoo. I got this on a whim when I went to Mitsuwa, because I liked the packaging. This particular type is great for short, tangled hair, but I find it works on my hair just fine.
